        <item>
            <title>Version 0.4.1</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 21:36:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>0.4.1</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.4.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixes pinned tabs (and occasionally the whole tab session) being wiped across restarts: a startup race could persist an empty snapshot before the saved session was restored.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
